title.rendered: Prishtina REA Leading the Way as Consortium Innovation Leader -CIL & Local Node – LN in Europe by empowering Innovation through Women led enterprises.

content.rendered:
Leading the Way as Consortium Innovation Leader -CIL & Local Node - LN in Europe by empowering Innovation through Women led enterprises.

Prishtina REA is selected as a CIL and LN under the project 𝐄𝐄𝐍𝟐𝐄𝐈𝐂, funded by European Commission for supporting 𝑺𝒆𝒂𝒍 𝒐𝒇 𝑬𝒙𝒄𝒆𝒍𝒍𝒆𝒏𝒄𝒆 holders.

EEN2EIC a European Union funded project aims to enhance collaboration and innovation by connecting businesses, particularly SMEs, with the European Innovation Council.

The project facilitates opportunities for businesses to access funding, support, and networking to promote innovation and growth in the European business landscape.
